                    Goal Met! {{campaign_title}}
                </h2>
                <p class="sub-title" style="color: #5b5b5b">
                    Dear {{first_name}} {{last_name}},
                </p>
                <p class="description" style="color: #5b5b5b ;font-size: 14px;">
                    Exciting news: we've achieved our goal for {{campaign_title}}, and it's all thanks to your
                    incredible
                    support! Your contribution is making a real difference and driving positive change.
                </p>

                <p style="color: #5b5b5b ;font-size: 14px;">Now that the campaign goal has been met, we're moving
                    forward to the manufacturing phase. Rest assured, we'll keep you informed once the delivery is
                    successfully completed.</p>
                <p style="color: #5b5b5b ;font-size: 14px;"> Your involvement and kindness are at the heart of this
                    success. Thank you for being an essential part of this journey.</p>

                <p style="color: #5b5b5b ;font-size: 14px;">
                    Best regards,<br>
                    Team Meththa Foundation
                </p>
                <br />
            </div>

        </div>
        <div style="background: #F2F0EC; padding: 20px 0px" ; class='container'>
